					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">I tried DKL2 and I see the glitches in the first water level. The game never crashed on me, but the level became so glitched that I could not complete it and eventually got stuck. I will investigate what is going on exactly.<br /><br />update: What appears to be happening is when you turn left or right while swimming in the water (or if you switch characters) it writes to the $5Axx range by use of a res nn,(hl) opcode. I think what ends up happening is it messes up the SmartCard's register, depending on where the game is stored on your card I guess glitches or a complete crash can happen. Again the bad thing with this game is that it has the fixed ROM bank packed to the max. This makes adding a patch harder.</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

